{"tid":1377843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武上撚晒腦、說好勇武後和理非接力呢、三不教條主義促成勇武鳩街磨爛席！","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:02:24.000Z","uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98218b1ea05196860f8ddcd378e8bc7fcb603447","tid":1377843,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">盡情屌我同起我底話知我係手足定係鬼！</span><br />\n我話知點樣突破！是靠和理非！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n香港人骨子裏嘅性格是膽小怕事。<br />\n難道無了期抗爭落去？<br />\n勇武拉嘅拉打嘅打，<br />\n和理非會漸漸麻木。<br />\n繼續等待視香港為籌碼嘅外國伸出緩手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭已經進入膠著狀態，<br />\n政府只要堅持一貫方針，<br />\n無力感只會不斷蔓延！<br />\n<br />\n下一步打贏呢場仗？<br />\n我地一直話呢場運動喚醒了千千萬萬個香港市民！<br />\n唯有罷工！至可以扭轉呢場屬性香港人嘅革命！<br />\n<br />\n罷工嘅威力是無庸置疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n612之後就罷工到宜家，我地一早贏撚左啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n若果沒六月丶七月嘅時代革命，<br />\n淺黃撚丶中立撚丶淺藍撚，<br />\n可能會幻想個政府仲有得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是每一次罷工只會是少數人以至流產 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每一次差嘅是咩？是信任！<br />\n同時差一班事前敢於發聲嘅參與者！<br />\n<br />\n故呼籲民陣食住個勢8月4日和理非總動員舉行，<br />\n全港罷工「前夕」大遊行！<br />\n倡議民陣係遊行設置大量街站，<br />\n讓參加者簽署聯署並要求參加者，<br />\n鄭重承諾將會由8月5日開始進行無了期罷工直至政府完成五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">提議一：蘊養基本參與人數<br />\n補充提議一：每一次遊行集會呼籲未簽署參與人士聯署<br />\n提議二：務必達到實時更新聯署人數<br />\n提議三：另特設公務員Booth/聯署表<br />\n提議四：冚世家打卡<br />\n提議五：事前吹到有幾大得幾大<br />\n補充提議五：呼籲市民購買一星期食物用品的長期抗爭<br />\n補充提議三：全民口罩護公務員、設置帳篷攤位<br />\n補充提議二：即場招募義工</span><br />\n </blockquote><br />\n[置頂] 倡議民陣搞全港罷工「前夕」大遊行，一齊罷工吧！香港人！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1375198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1375198</a>"},{"pid":"e32228fdb0afc902cbec32969a96c8436255d10b","tid":1377843,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43bfab8a0d867b41763500502f9ceb96c698678","tid":1377843,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daf1a23e2f8bc2706535512cc46283d0456b81e","tid":1377843,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4123744d279150be8c06dc8df0c65fe0e1054ce1","tid":1377843,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac66b9611c268332caf1046140c9eff232a7086","tid":1377843,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a91a2876d779d63e17ddfba57ae37c3db8842b","tid":1377843,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9dcfb1b1315622088070811b8074ee63458f655","tid":1377843,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:43:31.000Z","msg":"等收負評雨"},{"pid":"a057c7fa4631ea28cde0b1fd2563cf08e67a2319","tid":1377843,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"你D用字證明你係大陸人, 學下廣東話先la<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a209de4c285911574767bce319b56df0c6ad6e6e","tid":1377843,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"全部殺紅晒眼<br />\n又唔係真係打仗<br />\n人地可以換更黎捕你<br />\n你企係度唔知為乜"},{"pid":"a1e537901bde6556d7b6478fb370941df4c11df8","tid":1377843,"ui